{"tid":2440230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖雲達斯哭喪區 2021","createTime":"2021-03-09T22:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T01:11:14.000Z","uid":31024,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21a1c4f123798762b2a9031b9430ef44d14810f4","tid":2440230,"uid":31024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"死撚返出去啦死蛆狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你隊西波仲話劍指歐聯冠軍喎<br />\n<del>里昂</del>波圖都過唔撚到 返去食蕉啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時喺意甲有球證罩鳩住你地隊波就話蝦蝦霸霸恰鳩人姐<br />\n<del>一出到去球證幫少一陣都出事</del><br />\n<p class=\"left\"><p class=\"left\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n今次球證幫撚曬你喇 踢多一件都輸<br />\n你柒唔柒啲呀<br />\n<br />\n大佬踢葡超都輸 死入老母個閪啦</span></span></p></p><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7111e3ceebf4209868970c054bc4acdeb56fe9","tid":2440230,"uid":31024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:43:46.000Z","msg":"原Po:<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯球迷哭喪區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144976</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d11ff47a654d8676a48b7ce138c8f6c994da6716","tid":2440230,"uid":31024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:50:00.000Z","msg":"成場波2-1之後<br />\n打多個慢慢踢再俾人撳返住嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後輸球咁撚柒嘅罰球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑死人"},{"pid":"dc6754de09c5269a1bed7396a4ad4c42be9117bf","tid":2440230,"uid":61228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"今日係喜慶嘅一日"},{"pid":"30763dd5b3883f8b323bcd1cf1de4025ac66fdf6","tid":2440230,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy